{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_07_02",
  "title": "fran 2話 史上最悪の監督よ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――MV撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――MV Shooting Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 1.4200000048
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.4200000048
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……ナイトプールに大勢呼んで撮影しようだなんて\nkanaとは、とことん感性が合わないわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… calling a bunch of people to shoot at a night pool…\nI really don't share any sensibilities with kana…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "前は貸し切りだったし、優雅で良かったのに。しかも\nkanaの友達がエキストラとか、居心地悪過ぎますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was reserved before‚ and had a nice‚ elegant atmosphere.\nBut having kana's friends as extras makes it too uncomfortable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 20.3666669767
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "さっき早めに来ていた方々と、控室で話して\nましたよね？　和やかな雰囲気に見えましたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were talking with the people who came early\nin the waiting room‚ right? It looked harmonious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.7425335033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "あれは仕事の一環です\n笑顔を振りまくのが最低限のマナーですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was part of the job.\nSpreading smiles is the minimum courtesy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 33.20000031
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "というか、kanaの交友関係って\n一体どうなってるんですか？　節操なさ過ぎますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly‚ what’s going on with\nkana's social circle? It’s so all over the place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 39.8000020902
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "インフルエンサーの子達と延々と一緒に写真を\n撮らされたと思ったら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "One moment I’m being made to pose for endless pictures\nwith influencers‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.4531357286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "今度は大企業のかっちりした大人に\nご丁寧に名刺を渡されたりして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and the next I'm being handed business cards\nby stuffy corporate adults…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.8025628488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 48.3000005643
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "温度差も凄くて、気疲れしたんですけど……\nこの後、もっと増えるんですよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The temperature difference was huge and mentally exhausting…\nAnd more are coming later‚ right…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさん、顔が広いですからね\n俺もここまでいろんな人が来るとは思いませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "kana-san has a wide network.\nI didn't expect this many different people would come either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 60.4333338976
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "しかもみんなして律儀に挨拶に来るから\n余計にしんどいんですよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And they're all so diligent about coming to greet me\nwhich makes it even more exhausting…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～。早く帰ってサバイバル漫画の新刊が読みたい\n今すっごい面白いとこなのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh. I want to go home early and read the new survival manga.\nIt's at a really interesting part right now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 73.2666672309
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "撮影前からそんな悲しいことを言わないで下さい\nとりあえず、撮影の準備をしましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please don't say such sad things before shooting.\nFor now‚ let's prepare for shooting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 80.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "……ねぇ。なんで私達、こんな雑用をやらされてる訳？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey. Why are we being forced to do these menial tasks?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.6666687567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "人手が足りないからしょうがないですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're short-handed so it can't be helped.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.6666687567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 89.7000020901
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "だからって、機材の設営とかケーブルの配線とかまで\nやらされるのはおかしいでしょ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that doesn't mean we should be forced to do\nequipment setup and cable wiring!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "kanaのやつ、私をあごで使って！　しかも\nネチネチと細かいことにケチつけてくるんですよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That kana is ordering me around! And\nshe keeps nitpicking about every little detail!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 102.2333354234
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "姑か、って文句を言ってやったら「山田さんライトの\n隅に埃が残ってましてよ」とか余計に言ってくるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I complained \"Are you a mother-in-law?\" she said\n\"Yamada-san‚ there's dust remaining in the corner of the light.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 109.8333354234
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 115.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "ほんっっっとうに屈辱だわ！　史上最悪の監督よ！\nって……ああもう、また呼ばれるし。なんなのよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's reeeally humiliating! The worst director in history!\n…Ugh‚ I'm being called again. What now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10799.9979099,
          "startTime": 120.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "―― 一時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One hour later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.8592087029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 124.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "照明の位置的に、もう少しこっちから撮った方が\n衣装が映えていいかもしれないですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "From the lighting position‚ shooting a bit more from this side\nmight make the costumes stand out better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 131.600003616
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "そう……そんな感じです。ありがとうございます\nえぇ、これでもっと見栄えが良くなると思います！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… like that. Thank you.\nYes‚ I think this will look much better!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 139.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "あ、みなさん\nここは意外と段差があるので気を付けて下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ everyone‚\nthere are unexpected steps here so please be careful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 144.6333369493
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor018.m4a",
      "text": "意外と冷えますから、この毛布を使って下さい\n温かい飲み物はここにあるので、いつでも飲んで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It gets surprisingly cold‚ so please use this blanket.\nHot drinks are here‚ so please have them anytime.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-03.m4a",
          "delay": 1499.996383999985,
          "startTime": 146.1333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 152.400003616
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（franさん、不満はあるみたいだけど……）\n（エキストラを入れたシーンからは、切り替えてるな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（fran-san seems to have complaints‚ but…）\n（she's switched gears since the scenes with extras.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
