      "text": "本当は嫌ですよ。もっと撮影に集中したいですから\nでも……人手が足りないんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't actually like it. I want to focus more on shooting.\nBut… we're short-handed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 172.6333369493
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor020.m4a",
      "text": "これで円滑に進むなら、やるしかないじゃないですか\nいい作品を作るためなら、妥協は出来ないので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If this makes things go smoothly‚ then I have no choice but to do it.\nI can't compromise when it comes to making good work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor021.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんもちゃちゃっと動いて下さい\nなるべくスムーズにこの撮影を終わらせて……ん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So please move quickly too‚ {user}-san.\nLet's finish this shoot as smoothly as possible… hm?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
      "startTime": 187.4333369493
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor022.m4a",
      "text": "何よ、kana？　……はい？　「マネージャーと\nくっちゃべる暇があったらもっと必死で働け」……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What‚ kana? …Huh? \"If you have time to chat\nwith the manager‚ work more harder\"…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_02-kor023.m4a",
      "text": "ふ、ふふ、そうよね、人手が足りないものね\nわっかりました～。ふふ、ふふふふふ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fu‚ fufu‚ that's right‚ we're short-handed.\nI understaaand~. Fufu‚ fufufufufu…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
