      "text": "……ふぅ。撮影、順調に進んでますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Phew. The shooting is going smoothly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.2000127713,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
