      "text": "い、いやぁ、franさんのご協力のおかげですよ\n本当にありがとうございます。耐えていただいて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-well‚ it's thanks to your cooperation‚ fran-san.\nThank you so much. For enduring it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nightpool-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nightpool-00-night",
