      "text": "kanaにこき使われるのは、ほんとに腹立つけど……\n撮影さえ終われば解放されますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being bossed around by kana is really irritating‚ but…\nonce shooting ends‚ I'll be free.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
